Foxfingers followed the chosen ones to the Cybertronian Fire, he 
observes the size shape and armament of the ship. The red and brown 
bot reaches into a pack he carries with him and pulls out a 
minicomputer. Foxfingers taps in the information he sees and a 
picture of a ship very similar appears on the screen.

Pictures flickered across the screen, basic information on the 
warship in front of him was now at his disposal. The computer 
reported the ship as one of the many cruisers designed for 
exploration then turned into a warship when the Predacons came to 
power.

He opens a commlink with the ship "Um Hello my names Foxfingers I'm a 
maximal like you," he pointed to the emblem on his chest, even 
scarred as it was it was still visable. "Could someone give me some 
information on where we are and why theres so much activity on this 
planet?" His leader didn't have that information yet if FoxFingers 
was successful he soon would.
